OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1782492482
OL,3,CMan dies after entering the water at
OL,4,CAberavon beach
OL,6,FA 50-year-old man has died after
OL,7,Fentering the water at Aberavon beach,
OL,8,FSouth Wales Police has confirmed.
OL,10,FThe man, from the Neath Port Talbot
OL,11,Farea, went into the water on Wednesday
OL,12,F(24 June) afternoon. Emergency
OL,13,Fservices were then alerted to a man
OL,14,Fneeding medical assistance.
OL,16,FThe Coastguard, an air ambulance and
OL,17,Fparamedics attended the scene.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
