OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1782492482
OL,3,CMan dies after entering the water at
OL,4,CAberavon beach
OL,6,FA statement from South Wales Police
OL,7,Fread: "Officers were called to
OL,8,FAberavon Beach at around 4:25pm
OL,9,Fyesterday (Wednesday June 24)
OL,10,Ffollowing a report of a man requiring
OL,11,Fmedical assistance having entered the
OL,12,Fwater.
OL,14,F"The Coastguard commenced CPR until
OL,15,Fthe arrival of the air ambulance and
OL,16,Fparamedics. Despite the medical
OL,17,Fprofessionals' best efforts, the man -
OL,18,Fa 50-year-old man from Cilfrew, Neath
OL,19,FPort Talbot - was pronounced dead at
OL,20,Fthe scene at 4:50pm.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
