OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1782492482
OL,3,CMan dies after entering the water at
OL,4,CAberavon beach
OL,6,F"Next of kin has been informed. The
OL,7,Fdeath is not being treated as
OL,8,Fsuspicious."
OL,10,FOn Wednesday, a Welsh Ambulance
OL,11,FService spokesperson said: "We were
OL,12,Fcalled (on Wednesday) at approximately
OL,13,F4:07pm, to reports of a medical
OL,14,Femergency on Aberavon beach.
OL,16,F"We sent two Cymru High Acuity
OL,17,FResponse Units, one emergency
OL,18,Fambulance, a hazardous area response
OL,19,Fteam and an operations manager to the
OL,20,Fscene.
OL,26,@sD@\OUtD@HpmtD@UpnxD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
