OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1782492482
OL,3,CMan dies after entering the water at
OL,4,CAberavon beach
OL,6,F"Advanced critical care support was
OL,7,Fdelivered by the Emergency Medical
OL,8,FRetrieval and Transfer Service in a
OL,9,FWales Air Ambulance charity
OL,10,Fhelicopter."
OL,12,FIt comes as Wales enters a second day
OL,13,Fof extreme heat, as a red weather
OL,14,Fwarning is in place until midnight on
OL,15,FThursday (25 June). Temperatures could
OL,16,Fsoar as high as 36C in parts of south
OL,17,FWales.
